CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 19, 1939, pg. 13, reads: "..And the Merry-Go-Round Didn't Break Down... At the Frog picnic in Olympia park, Pittsburgh, the delightfully young enjoyed rides on the merry-go-round. Here are pictured on their sturdy steeds, Marva Louis, left; Katherine King and Portia Trotter, Marva's sister, all of Chicago.  And the merry-go-round did not break down."
TitMainTitle: Singer Marva Louis riding carousel horse, with Katherine King and Portia Trotter in background, at FROGS Club picnic, Olympia Park, McKeesport
